class of consumed posit instances), and value σ in an intrinsic degree structure
(Lawvere–Tierney local operators / Weihrauch degrees) in which EM/LPO/MP/LLPO are
DEFINABLE LANDMARKS, not the codomain. The immediately load-bearing probe (the
